{"tid":1256562,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（集合市民體諒既報導）市民稱：很支持他們／支持年輕人這份熱情","createTime":"2019-06-25T05:44:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-25T06:20:26.000Z","uid":50275,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"25efc2fdd1d06bd7427ebcd8bf0564fb6e127f33","tid":1256562,"uid":50275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T05:44:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/1WkBBm4q3PY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F1WkBBm4q3PY&d=DgFN9ivcdgICzBQxXV443irXKCTJ71YGEIw5q99tfRY%3D&h=d716a1d6\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/1WkBBm4q3PY</a> <br />\n<br />\n有司機指：「開回一條路，可不可以？開回一條路，我們走。多謝你們，我支持你們的，記著。」<br />\n<br />\n示威者自行指揮交通，重開部分行車線。<br />\n<br />\n另一名司機稱：「我很支持他們，我一定支持他們，問題是這個香港政府，簡直不知所謂，你要回應別人，做『縮頭龜』有何用？」<br />\n<br />\n另一名司機說：「逼年青人出來，然後逼他們暴力，就更暴力對付他們，逼到民怨更大。其實政府要解決這個問題。」<br />\n<br />\n王先生指出：「每個行動都會影響一些人，如果沒有影響就不會有成果。如果可以，我向受阻人士，代年輕人為他們道歉，但我們一定要支持年輕人這份熱情。」"},{"pid":"c62b3b64a867f9cbe4279a460a9cdc68fcfe6016","tid":1256562,"uid":50275,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T05:44:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/06/25/g6oSQP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F06%2F25%2Fg6oSQP.png&h=a813af03&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/06/25/be3KiN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F06%2F25%2Fbe3KiN.png&h=44dc5bc0&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/06/25/MCXyhk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F06%2F25%2FMCXyhk.png&h=9ec08010&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/06/25/i5yXzY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F06%2F25%2Fi5yXzY.png&h=84238369&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/06/25/td2mNX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F06%2F25%2Ftd2mNX.png&h=14121539&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/06/25/T8WRPy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F06%2F25%2FT8WRPy.png&h=77b851a5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5e52ddfd6f79f8340ed30b2e7075f11cd43c9ab2","tid":1256562,"uid":50275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T05:44:58.000Z","msg":"仲有無人知有其他報導"},{"pid":"76f4d8167ccc00b41b016dd907d7dc67e33cd783","tid":1256562,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T05:51:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />睇到呢啲明白事理既長輩就好感動"},{"pid":"d307b02fa0f4fd4606918fccc504ce76c3cce3a5","tid":1256562,"uid":50275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5e52ddfd6f79f8340ed30b2e7075f11cd43c9ab2","tid":1256562,"uid":50275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T05:44:58.000Z","msg":"仲有無人知有其他報導"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T06:01:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ba222c7efa9e521693af262bdd4bf89915588fc","tid":1256562,"uid":1623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T06:16:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dce9080c47392ba3f3067d5363010cec782d64e4","tid":1256562,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T06:18:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">這就是民意</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"050745135db9850e6a58ffb0083d76ca636874e1","tid":1256562,"uid":50275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T06:20:26.000Z","msg":"有無人記得咩電視台有同樣報導？"}]}